“柏林可能封城或部分封城”。
"Berlin may be sealed off or partially sealed."
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
余鹏/央视新闻客户端央视新闻客户端2月26日消息，德国联邦参议院参议员安德烈亚斯·盖塞尔（Andreas Geisel）25日表示，鉴于新冠肺炎病毒可能在欧洲流行，柏林可能封城或者部分封城。
BERLIN (Reuters) - German Federal Senate Senator Andreas Geisel said Thursday that Berlin could be closed or partially closed down with the possibility of a new outbreak of the virus in Europe.
盖塞尔表示，柏林已经采取了适当的民事防护措施，制定了相应的计划。
Mr Gessel said Berlin had taken appropriate civil protection measures and planned accordingly.
但如果情况危急，柏林将采取类似于意大利北部城市封城得措施。
But in case of emergency, Berlin would take measures similar to those imposed on northern Italian cities.
盖塞尔强调，至于是否封城以及在多大程度上实施如此严厉的措施尚待观察。
Mr Gessell stressed that it remained to be seen whether and to what extent such draconian measures would be imposed.
当天，德国卫生部长斯潘在罗马表示，即使意大利爆发疫情，也不应该禁止跨境旅行。
On the same day, German Health Minister Jospin said in Rome that cross-border travel should not be banned even in the event of an outbreak in Italy.
截至记者发稿时，意大利确诊新型冠状病毒肺炎病例已增至322例，其中10人死亡，1人治愈出院。
By the time of writing, the number of confirmed cases of coronavirus pneumonia in Italy had risen to 322, 10 of them dead and one cured.
本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
